{"tid":1681680,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"抗共輿論戰要開波喇","createTime":"2019-10-29T14:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:48:33.000Z","uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0df6b8facf2b0716da9d21d5b6fcc0f94e28ca7c","tid":1681680,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"親中媒體不斷透過抹黑民主派侯選人，一直不遺餘力。<br />\n<br />\n我哋係時候要還擊了。<br />\n以彼之道，還施彼身<br />\n應該馬上徵用各區連儂牆<br />\n大肆宣揚班保皇建制<br />\n係點撚樣出賣香港人<br />\n主要對象應該要集中係老人家身上，例如整多啲長輩圖。<br />\n中年嗰批人就儘量放多啲實質證據出嚟，令佢哋相信。<br />\n<br />\n新一輪抗共輿論戰要展開了，你班連登仔準備好未？"},{"pid":"498d3c6f5d4b3fc3cd41f4118cbf55eb0a10979f","tid":1681680,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPMCZAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPMCZAr.jpg&h=a189dd43&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ada8b61165836aa42afe8918a41a293e31b2621","tid":1681680,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89248fd7736fb716e48ab0ab40d21df2fefb8da9","tid":1681680,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"推"}]}